		<RichText x="738" y="223" width="414" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">斩风侧举大剑，进行至多3段的普通攻击，依次造成<span color="#7fffd7">60%,80%,80%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="479" width="424" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">斩风扯开大剑，转身甩出6个旋转的碎片，造成<span color="#7fffd7">40%,16%,4%</span><span>伤害，然后再收回，甩出和收回均造成</span><span color="#7fffd7">60%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="735" width="424" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">斩风抖开大剑，然后朝前方猛击，每个造成<span color="#7fffd7">100%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/黑蛇骑士%B7斩风之剑.assets/Image_13.png')" x="720" y="137">
		</BitmapImage>
