		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/黑蛇骑士%B7斩风之剑.assets/Image_15.png')" x="720" y="650">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/黑蛇骑士%B7斩风之剑.assets/Image_16.png')" x="596" y="683" blendMode="normal">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/黑蛇骑士%B7斩风之剑.assets/Image_17.png')" x="576" y="662" blendMode="normal">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/黑蛇骑士%B7斩风之剑.assets/Image_18.png')" x="1392" y="137">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/黑蛇骑士%B7斩风之剑.assets/Image_19.png')" x="1392" y="394">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/黑蛇骑士%B7斩风之剑.assets/Image_20.png')" x="1390" y="650">
		</BitmapImage>
		<RichText x="1410" y="223" width="439" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">斩风拿着大剑蓄力，进行至多2段的普通攻击，都造成<span color="#7fffd7">80%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="479" width="439" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">斩风正举大剑，将6个剑刃碎片依次发射出来，每个造成<span color="#7fffd7">30%</span><span>伤害。<br/>该状态下，抗打断0。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="735" width="441" height="200" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">当斩风的攻击命中护盾庇护下的的玩家时，<span color="#72ffb8">扣除当前15%生命值</span><span>，自己将获得一层「敏捷」：受攻击时闪现免伤，闪现后</span><span color="#ffbfbf">获得30%攻击力提升，该提升在造成一次伤害或施放完一次技能后消失</span><span>。「敏捷」会在闪现一次后或者持续10s后消失，至多叠加一层。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="899" y="62" fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="normal" color="#00ae83" width="207" height="28" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="1">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" color="#00ae83">制图@Csxylic米游社</p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="72" y="497" fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W04" fontSize="40" fontStyle="italic" fontWeight="normal" color="#99ffe5" width="446" height="43" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="1">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W04" fontSize="40" fontStyle="italic" color="#99ffe5">「曾经行于微风之中…」</p>
			</content>
